  smash -z <inputs>               encode with zstd (fast modern, opt-in)
  smash --ai <inputs>             native semantic compress + xz (lossy)
  smash --ai-api <inputs>         LLM API compress + xz (lossy, ~5-10%)
  smash -d <artifact> [...]       decode artifacts (auto-detects format,
                                  extracts dirs, strips v5 manifest,
                                  reads pre-v5 headerless artifacts)
